data.description: Welcome to the perfect family home at 30302 Blue Cedar Drive in beautiful Menifee, California! This spacious and inviting residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a generous 2,855 square feet of living space, providing plenty of room for both comfort and style.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open  floor plan that's perfect for modern living. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample pantry and cabinet space. Whether you're cooking for a family dinner or hosting a gathering, this kitchen is a chef's delight.    Upstairs, you'll find the spacious bedrooms, each offering a retreat of its own. The master suite is a true sanctuary, featuring an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. The master suite boasts of a large separate retreat area and on suite. Besides the bedroom the home also has a separate office area and a bonus loft. With three additional bedrooms, there's room for everyone in the family or the flexibility to create a home office or gym.    One of the standout features of this property is its location within the Pacific Mayfield community, which ensures access to amenities and a well-maintained environment. The community park is not just a place; it's a vibrant gathering point for all ages, fostering connections, promoting wellness, and celebrating the beauty of our community.     Located in the developing city of Menifee, you'll have easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and recreational opportunities. Don't miss your chance to make 30302 Blue Cedar Drive your new home and experience the best of Southern California living.
